// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3393 — Mass File Rename (ransomhub)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 64292362-5076-5626-9993-c63c95aa082f

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
